title: Magic Rhine: from its source to the North sea. DVD5
description:
Join us on a journey down the Rhine, from the source of the river in the Swiss Alps to its estuary in the North Sea.

On the way we stop in Liechtenstein, Meersburg on Lake Constance, at the Rhine Falls of Schaffhausen and in Basel. Then we visit the wine-growing area of the Kaiserstuhl, the cities of Strasbourg, Speyer and Worms as well as the state capital, Mainz.

Our journes end at the North Sea coast in Rotterdam.
